config.DatabaseQuery:
SELECT metric AS jobId, (CASE 
	 WHEN duration > 24 THEN CONCAT(round(duration/24), 'd ago')
    ELSE CONCAT(duration, 'h ago') END) AS lastBuild,  status FROM (
SELECT NOW(),finishedOn, round(time_to_sec(timediff(NOW(), finishedOn )) / 3600) AS duration, 
jobId AS  metric, status
FROM jobs WHERE stage='build' AND STATUS NOT IN('skipped')
ORDER BY createdOn DESC LIMIT 5) AS a1;
